      "text": "# 📖 Act 18: Mirror in Dust\n**act** · first_person · narrative · first_person\n\nVibed into Scrying Glass. Ask 'what vibrates?' not 'what harms?'"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "2d76f4f0c40a3fbd",
      "text": "> *The mirror that only shows the whole scroll past reveals nothing; the scrying that shows affinity is where the seeker becomes the mage.*"
